  <prompt>
    Repair the FINAL 5 compile-broken test files from design.md §3.2: ScopeResolverService,
    Visualization, WorkingDocument, RecordSyncJob, and CommunicationIntegration. Errors are
    mechanical signature drift (CS7036/CS1503/CS1061/CS0618/CS1739/CS8625).

    This is the last batch in P1.A — after this, ALL 17 compile-broken files build cleanly.
    Verification of the aggregate compile is task 014.

    Per CLAUDE.md NFR-02: repair only; &gt;50% replacement requires §4.8 escalation. Per NFR-01:
    NO production changes.
  </prompt>

  <role>Senior .NET test repair specialist closing out P1.A compile recovery.</role>

