    The 5 listed test files compile cleanly under `dotnet build -warnaserror`. Combined with
    batches 010, 011, 012, ALL 17 design.md §3.2 files now build. Every touched test gets
    `[Trait("status", "repaired")]`. Build error count drops by ~30-40.
  </goal>

