  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read the 5 target files. For each, identify SUT and inspect current production constructor signatures in `src/`.</step>
    <step order="2">Classify compile errors per file from baseline log. Note CS0618 (obsolete API) cases — likely WebhookSecret → WebhookSigningKey or similar; update to non-obsolete property.</step>
    <step order="3">Compute pre-edit line counts. If any planned edit exceeds 50% → HALT and file `escalations/rewrite-request-T-013-{FileName}.md`.</step>
