    <step order="7">Final compile gate: `dotnet build tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/ -c Release -warnaserror` returns 0 on the 5 target files.</step>
    <step order="8">Update `current-task.md` with per-file LOC delta + announce expected zero compile errors after batches 010+011+012+013 complete.</step>
    <step order="9">Verify `git status` shows NO production modifications.</step>
  </steps>

